## Configure OpenAPI document generation

The following code:

*   Adds OpenAPI services using the [AddOpenApi](/en-us/dotnet/api/microsoft.extensions.dependencyinjection.openapiservicecollectionextensions.addopenapi) extension method on the app builder's service collection.
*   Maps an endpoint for viewing the OpenAPI document in JSON format with the [MapOpenApi](/en-us/dotnet/api/microsoft.aspnetcore.builder.openapiendpointroutebuilderextensions.mapopenapi) extension method on the app.

```
var builder = WebApplication.CreateBuilder();

